'''Rust and oxidation lubricant''' ('''R&O''') is a mild [[lubricant]] treated with [[corrosion inhibitor]]s. The [[oil]] is used mainly for [[Bearing (mechanical)|bearing]] and lightly loaded [[gearbox]] applications.

[[Turbine]] oil is classiflied as R&O but the quality is much higher.

